{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 A major point of contention was the hospitals\rquote  agreement that the Catholic Ethical and Religious Directives would apply to all corporate entities, thereby eliminating access to certain reproductive health services that had previously been provided by the secular hospital.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F78303574216_ID0EL5AG_2}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F78303574216_ID0EL5AG_2}
