{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
As is the case with for-profit businesses (and probably more so), agency problems make the issue of accountability the central problem that must be addressed by nonprofit organizational law.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F126303574216_ID0EJRBG_2}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F126303574216_ID0EJRBG_2}
