*34
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 with exactness in either the entity\rquote s charter or the law.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F129303574216_ID0EWTBG_2}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F129303574216_ID0EWTBG_2}
