129
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The fundamental objective of fiduciary duties in the corporate context, then, is to bind managers to serve their principals\rquote  interests and thereby overcome the high agency costs inherent in the corporate form.
}
