{\b1 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb200 
B. Applying the Fiduciary Duties to Commercial Nonprofits in the Health Care Sector
\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
