{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EM4BG_2}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EM4BG_2}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Despite the inadequacies associated with applying corporate law to the nonprofit context, it has become the template for all state nonprofit statutes.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F154303574216_ID0EU4BG_2}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F154303574216_ID0EU4BG_2}
