{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EV5BG_2}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EV5BG_2}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
The duty of care is traditionally characterized by a three-part test 
}
