155
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The important caveat that the decision be the product of an informed judgment limits somewhat the rule\rquote s potentially all-encompassing sweep and bars its application in situations of nonfeasance.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F156303574216_ID0EQ6BG_2}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F156303574216_ID0EQ6BG_2}
