{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 In addition, recent decisions by some courts suggest that boards that consciously disregard risks fail to satisfy the \u8220\'3fgood faith\u8221\'3f requirement and will not enjoy the rule\rquote s protection.
