}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 primarily wealth maximization. The question then becomes whether the corporate notion of the duty of loyalty can be usefully reformulated to ensure appropriate director behavior and preservation of the charitable mission in the nonprofit context.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
