{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
The duty of loyalty also governs the individual board member\rquote s relations with the corporation of which she is a director. Interestingly, neither courts nor legislatures have interpreted the duty of loyalty in the for-profit context as prohibiting outright self-dealing and other conflicted interest transactions.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F163303574216_ID0ERCAI_2}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F163303574216_ID0ERCAI_2}
