{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Thus, it is uncontroversial that if a nonprofit hospital corporation is sold, converts, or dissolves, it must treat separately any trust property it received during its existence, ensuring that in its capacity as trustee, it is faithful to the settlor\rquote s intent.
