{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Typically, however, the assets of a health care corporation have been acquired or built from myriad sources, including the entity\rquote s profits, bond issues, tax subsidies, governmental aid 
}
