{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0ETICI_2}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0ETICI_2}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
In this environment, it is important to remember the norm-shaping impact of law. As scholarship has stressed, an important objective of the law is to shift social norms and social meaning.
}
