{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Finally, we consider the law of nonprofits from an institutional perspective. Attorneys general play a complicated role in the current environment. They fill a variety of roles with respect to the nonprofit sector: prosecutor, consumer advocate, public representative as parens patriae, supervisor of charitable trusts, regulator, and politically accountable officer of the state.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F284303574216_ID0E2JCI_2}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F284303574216_ID0E2JCI_2}
