{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Abhorring a vacuum, many have assumed a multi-faceted role in the oversight of the governance of 
}
{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
{\*\bkmkstart co_pp_sp_155362_80_2}{\*\bkmkend co_pp_sp_155362_80_2}
