*81
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 spawned uncertainty in business planning that may weaken the nonprofit sector\rquote s ability to serve its societal purposes. Finally, ambiguity about the role of boards and attorneys general may have diverted health policymakers and regulators from dealing squarely with the central task of fairly and efficiently allocating charitable assets.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
