 appropriate risk-taking. Finally, mission primacy accounts for the particular circumstances of nonprofit governance because it preserves the central values of trust and volunteerism that are needed to reinforce legal duties.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
