{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0E2UCI_2}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0E2UCI_2}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
In cases involving organic change, such as the hospital closure at issue in MEETH, mission primacy would mandate consideration of and deference to the board\rquote s evaluation of mission, and its determination of the most appropriate means to accomplish that mission.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
