Section 8.30 of the Revised Model Nonprofit Corporation Act adopts the standard of conduct almost identical to that of the Revised Model Business Act:
\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
