[D]irector shall discharge his or her duties as a director, including his or her duties as a member of a committee: (1) in good faith; (2) with the care of an ordinarily prudent person in a like position would exercise in similar circumstances; and (3) in a manner the director reasonably believes to be in the best interest of the corporation.
\par 
}
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
